---
title: Caribbean-Inspired Pork Tacos with Pineapple, Slaw and Cilantro Crema
description: Jerk-spiced pork will leave you salivating for more! From the fresh pineapple, to the citrusy slaw and cilantro crema, mix and match your favourite toppings!
